      <title>美国基金在敖德萨谷物码头纠纷中赢得乌克兰法院支持</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-04/us-funds-win-ukraine-court-support-in-odesa-grain-terminal-spat</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国基金 Argentem Creek Partners 和 Innovatus Capital Partners 表示，他们已赢得乌克兰法院的支持，试图从当地金融家手中夺取敖德萨一家谷物码头运营商的控制权。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-04/us-funds-win-ukraine-court-support-in-odesa-grain-terminal-spat</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 04 Apr 2024 16:08:50 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
