      <title>俄罗斯因贸易争端扣留两艘埃及小麦船</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-04/russia-holds-up-two-egyptian-wheat-ships-due-to-trader-dispute</link>
      <description><![CDATA[俄罗斯当局扣押了两艘满载出口小麦的埃及船只，这是一个主要谷物贸易商与农业监管机构之间的国内争端正在阻碍向国外交货的最新迹象。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-04/russia-holds-up-two-egyptian-wheat-ships-due-to-trader-dispute</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 04 Apr 2024 15:50:46 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
